%, which includes the impact of the discount upon issuance. The 2024 senior notes will mature on May 15, 2024 , and i nterest has accrued on the 2024 senior notes from May 16, 2017 and is paid in cash on May 15 and November 15 of each year. The net proceeds from this offering, after deducting underwriter discounts and commissions and estimated offering expenses, were $ 644 million and were used to pay down amounts outstanding under the RCF and for general corporate purposes. 

